The HTTP API is for direct debugging, JSON collection, and easy Node.js integration.

The gRPC API is for persistent streaming and dynamic sampling changes.

The agent should maintain the latest snapshot in memory. HTTP requests should normally return cached/latest data quickly rather than running expensive commands every time.

