Disk classification rule:

```text
if tran == "nvme" or name starts with nvme -> NVMe SSD
else if rota == false and tran in ["sata", "sas"] -> SATA/SAS SSD
else if rota == true -> HDD
else if model/vendor contains RAID -> RAID Logical Disk
else if type == lvm -> LVM Logical Volume
else Unknown
```

Do not blindly mark RAID as HDD or SSD unless rotation/transport/sysfs gives enough signal.

